that is working with an alien civilization to control the island and everyone who lives on it.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316130/extras/a749ce552c41148492a2124ed9817b92.poster.avif?t=1757463377\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316130/extras/a749ce552c41148492a2124ed9817b92.webm?t=1757463377\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316130/extras/a749ce552c41148492a2124ed9817b92.mp4?t=1757463377\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Zede escapes his cell only to discover his dream has inexplicably become a reality and he is forced to live inside it. Help Zede wander through Lavender Corporate City by collecting masks with different abilities and ships that help enable him to move quickly from neighborhood to neighborhood as he engages with Lavender’s inhabitants, falls in love, and uncovers layers of lore revolving around the island’s mysterious history and various cultures.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316130/extras/6a448bc8ee70091a669fa7cab1b396cc.poster.avif?t=1757463377\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316130/extras/6a448bc8ee70091a669fa7cab1b396cc.webm?t=1757463377\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316130/extras/6a448bc8ee70091a669fa7cab1b396cc.mp4?t=1757463377\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
